      "details": {
        "message": {
          "id": "1510894538347253781",
          "content": "@everyone\n\n# \ud83c\udf0a MAJOR STAFF UPDATE \ud83c\udf0a\nWe've completely overhauled how staffing works in Wave, a brand-new hub, Power roles, and a massive economy rebalance.\n\n\ud83d\udd17 **It's all in one place:** https://wavedropmaps.github.io/wave-leaderboard/\n\n**__\ud83d\udda5\ufe0f THE NEW WAVE STAFF HUB__**\nOne link for everything \u2014 live leaderboards, the economy, the shop, and a guide for every board:\n\ud83d\udccb Staff Sheet \u00b7 \ud83c\udfc6 Lifetime Activity \u00b7 \u2694\ufe0f Weekly Activity \u00b7 \ud83d\udcb0 Economy \n\n----------------------------------------------------------\n\u2753 Every board has a **`? GUIDE`** button (top-right) \u2014 tap it for the system with a visual explanation\n- Example provided in images below!\n----------------------------------------------------------\n\n**__\u26a1 NEW: Power Tiers & Roles for the Lifetime Activity section __**\nEvery badge you earn \u2014 on **any** duty \u2014 builds your **Power Score**. Hit the thresholds for an exclusive **Discord role + a one-time WP bonus**:\n\ud83e\udd49 Bronze 4pts \u2192 +20 \u00b7 \ud83e\udd48 Silver 8 \u2192 +50 \u00b7 \ud83e\udd47 Gold 16 \u2192 +100 \u00b7 \ud83c\udf1f Legend 32 \u2192 +300 \u00b7 \ud83d\udc51 God 64 \u2192 +500 WP\n\n**__\ud83d\udc8e WAVE POINTS SHOP \u2014 50% PRICE CUT__**\n\ud83c\udf0a Pro Surge Route \u2192 **200 WP**\n\ud83d\udcb0 Pro Loot Route \u2192 **400 WP**\n\ud83c\udfaf Pro Drop Map \u2192 **700 WP**\n\u2b50 Paid Priority \u2192 **400 WP**\n\ud83c\udf0a Wave Contributor \u2192 **450 WP**\n\ud83d\udc51 VIP \u2192 **5,000 WP**\n\n**__\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f LOOT ROUTE POINTS \u2014 4\u00d7 EARN RATES__**\n\u26a1 Within 12h \u2192 **10 pts** (was 2.5)\n\u26a1 Within 24h \u2192 **8 pts** (was 2)\n\ud83c\udfc3 Within 48h \u2192 **4 pts** (was 1)\n\ud83d\udeb6 Within 3 days \u2192 **2 pts** (was 0.5)\n\ud83d\udc80 Late penalty is now **descending** \u2014 -4 day 1, -3 day 2, -2 day 3, then -1/day\n*(Loot route prizes have gone up as a result!)*\n\n**__\ud83d\udcb1 CURRENCY EXCHANGE \u2014 REBALANCED__**\nLoot Route Points are now stronger vs Wave Points \u2014 baseline raised to **1 LRP = 4 WP** (was 1.67).\n\n**__\ud83c\udfc6 ROLE GIVER WEEKLY \u2014 BIGGER PRIZES__**\n\ud83e\udd47 1st \u2192 **700 VBucks** (was 500)\n\ud83e\udd48 2nd \u2192 **400 VBucks** (was 300)\n\ud83e\udd49 3rd \u2192 **200 VBucks** (unchanged)\n\n\ud83d\udd17 **Check the full leaderboard & shop:** https://wavedropmaps.github.io/wave-leaderboard/?v=2\n\n\n`Another major post coming in 24 hours.`",
